I agree with Logo, that post was kinda .... crap.

::Prowl/Zardus/Reptilica/Bloodystrike/Mosquitor::

Prowl goes into another spiral, continous shots hitting nothing but air. He 
takes in a breath as Iron Raptor clings to him, his mind once again 
wandering, thinking of how she felt pressed to him. She smelled pretty good 
too...

He snaps his mind back to the battle as two discs sink into his leg, a 
missile hitting him in the back. He recovers from plummeting down at the 
trees, rising once again in altitude.

"My balance is just fine," he says, stopping suddenly in the air, a few shots 
passing in front of him, as well as Reptilica. Prowl aims his gun, firing a 
shot at the bot's jetpack. The shot hits, Reptilica screaming as he drops 
down toward the forest, his jetpack going out.

He
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus enters the Alliance base, recieving Double Punch's transmission.

"Very well," he replies, then setting his comm-link to transmit to all 
Alliance members, "Everyone, try not to kill the Predacons too much. Unless 
they fire on you or you really want to."

He continues to walk down the hallway. It was no concern to him what happened 
at the battle, just as long as there were some casualties.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike continues to run at Dinobot, firing.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor, too dumb to realize that the Alliance was also going at the 
Maximals, fires his acid at Scattershot, flying at the Alliance bot.
